episodes.title: Prosecution pushing for parents of Elizabeth Struhs to be jailed for 15 years
14 cult members found guilty of the manslaughter of an 8-year-old girl | 7NEWS
episodes.description:
14 members of a Queensland religious cult are now confirmed killers, found guilty of the manslaughter of a little girl. 8-year-old Elizabeth Struhs died after members of the group withheld her life saving medication, believing that God would intervene.
